description:
Big changes are in store now that Moritaka and Akito have their very own series in Shonen Jump. Hanging out with their favorite manga creators, hiring assistants, keeping track of the weekly reader surveys--life as a professional manga artist is tough! Can these two survive the pressure?

Chapter Titles

  • Ch. 35: Happiness and Sadness
  • Ch. 36: Silence and Party
  • Ch. 37: Executive Director and Songbird
  • Ch. 38: Window and Snow
  • Ch. 39: Yearbook and Photobook
  • Ch. 40: Beach and Ups and Downs
  • Ch. 41: Pandering and Patience
  • Ch. 42: Humor and Dialogue
  • Ch. 43: Jokes and News
name: Yearbook and Photobook

description:
Dark times have fallen on our heroes as Grace, Malikai, Sonia, and PJ have all taken separate paths following the devastating battle at the end of SOULFIRE Volume 2.

Grace finds herself attempting to hold together the kingdom of the Everlands, as a theft in the hallowed halls of Anantia threatens to weaken the bonds between the Rahtumi and Sethoru once more.

While Grace struggles to keep unity between the two races, Malikai, the bearer of the light, is nowhere to be found. After unleashing his frightening levels of power during the final battle, Malikai deserts the group as he searches within for answers.

But, Rainier's forces persist in their quest to exterminate the return of the light as one of his most trusted allies soon discovers a darker form of magic in the process... with deadly results!

New adversaries, exotic locations, and a fresh cast of exciting character, including some from the Soulfire Universe's long forgotten past, reign supreme in this debut of the epic third SOULFIRE volume!

Grace has confrontation with Onyx and Malikai wonders into Siberia.
name: Seeds of Darkness

description:
We ARE all lost!

Ray rescued Madeline from the clutches of the City's criminal underworld, but nothing is what it seems. Where in the hell did those demonic thugs come from? And, what do they want from Madeline?

As the veil peels revealing the true face of the City, Ray will be confronted with the ultimate decision: Save himself or save everyone?

But, when everything you've known is suddenly a lie, where do you find the truth?
With civil war looming, Major Beck tries to maintain his foothold in Jericho as Jake and Hawkins return home-with the master terrorist John Smith!
name: Foes Become Friends

description: Since enrolling at Morning Glory Academy, perhaps no new student has been through more than Jade. But it turns out, sadly, this is one girl who is no stranger to pain and suffering - learn more about who she is, what she's been through, and what the Academy wants with her right here!

From the lead writer of the Crysis 2 video game! Set in the world of the award-winning Crysis games comes the newest hit series from EA Comics! Earth, 2020. United States Special Forces Major Laurence 'Prophet' Barnes and the soldiers of Raptor Team thought their deployment on the Lingshan islands was a basic covert op against North Korean forces. But they couldn't be more wrong. What archaeologists awakened on the island had lain buried for millions of years, and was utterly hostile to human life. Now an alien race are stirring, first contact has turned into humanity's worst nightmare, and Prophet's squad are the last remaining survivors. Only one real question remains - can Prophet get his people off Lingshan alive, and back to civilization in time to warn the rest of the human race what's on its way.

Wolverine invades a Hydra base on a mission of mercy but mercy isn't what hell be showing the soldiers he finds!

By Christopher Yost, Robert Kirkman, Craig Kyle, Jason Pearson and Carlo Barberi.

Also: Logan battles terrorists on a 747 flying into disaster!

By William Harms, Tomm Coker and Jefte Palo.

Plus: Deadpool dines with Death, argues with a talking shark and hits San Francisco hard!

By Daniel Way and Paco Medina.

Collects:

  • Deadpool (2008) #15
  • Wolverine: The Anniversary (2009) #1
  • X-Force (2008) Annual 01

Wolverine faces a final showdown with the deadly Adamantium Men!

By Jason Aaron and Ron Garney

Also: A swarm of Hydra agents attack and Wolverine must fight them while blinded!

By Mike Carey and Scott Kolins.

Plus: Deadpools dreams of becoming a pirate are fulfilled as he sets sail to battle the evil Captain Wackbeard!

By Daniel Way and Shawn Crystal.

Includes material reprinted from:

  • Deadpool (2008) #14
  • Wolverine: Firebreak (2008) #1
  • Wolverine: Weapon X (2009) #5

The Adamantium Men! Wolverine clashes with a squad of ruthless mercenaries all armed with healing factors and claws!

By Jason Aaron and Ron Garney.

Waves of Mutilation! Deadpool has a ton of money and a new goal in life: hes gonna be a pirate!

By Daniel Way and Shawn Crystal.

Includes material reprinted from:

  • Deadpool (2008) #13
  • Wolverine: Weapon X (2009) #3
  • Wolverine: Weapon X (2009) #4

A new story begins! Wolverine uncovers a conspiracy to create a new breed of super-soldiers: the Adamantium Men! Dont miss the start of an action-packed saga!

By Jason Aaron, Ron Garney, Marko Djurdjevic, Adam Kubert, Alan Davis, and Olivier Coipel.

Also: Deadpool and Bullseye go face-to-fist in the craziest duel youve ever seen!

By Daniel Way, Paco Medina and Marte Gracia.

Includes material reprinted from:

  • Deadpool (2008) #11
  • Deadpool (2008) #12
  • Wolverine: Weapon X (2009) #1
  • Wolverine: Weapon X (2009) #2

At last... Wolverine fights the villain who has controlled his entire life: Romulus!!! Dont miss a brutal battle!

By Daniel Way and Scot Eaton.

Also: Spider-Man confronts Logan as he falls into the depths of despair can Spidey save his fellow Avenger?

By Daniel Way, Jason Aaron, Adam Kubert and Tommy Lee Edwards.

Plus: Norman Osborn aims a new assassin in Deadpools direction: his old buddy Bullseye!

By Daniel Way and Paco Medina.

Includes material reprinted from: Wolverine Origins #40, Wolverine 73-74 and Deadpool #10.

'KING OF THE JUNGLE'

It's hard telling the predators from the prey in part three of this fast, funny 100% cool new series! Up-and-coming mobsters Alyosha the Lion and Tony Luciano think they're kings of the jungle...but their reign may be cut short by forces on both sides of the law.

********************************

Wimoweh, a-wimoweh...in the village, the peaceful village, nobody sleeps tonight! Steroid-pumped civilians face off against style-obsessed mobsters...a surveillance team realizes theyre being staked out by a mysterious intruder...and ruthless young lions stalk the kings of the criminal jungle. Who lives, who dies...and what would the Hoff do? Its hard telling the predators from the prey in part three of Image Comics smash hit new crime series!
name: King of the Jungle

description: DINOSAURUS returns! Hellbent on righting what he sees as wrong in the world he comes face-to-face with Invincible and the result is devastating.

A deformed creature stalks the dark alleys of Green Wake in search of the murderer, its motivations unclear. With the lead suspect in danger of disappearing, Morley stumbles upon a resident who bestows upon him a powerful vision, unlocking a grisly glimpse into a series of events that could change his life forever.

ENTER: THUNDER HEAD

Malcolm Dragon's life is in a shambles--things have gone from crazy to insane and things couldn't look much more bleak--or so he thought. Enter: Thunder Head--the satanic son of one of his father's most fiendish foes! Comes with our highest possible recommendation!
name: Falling Down

description: Martin, Java and Diana are in Italy, where a crazy murderer kills in the ruins of Etruscan Viterbo . He is convinced to be the reincarnation of the ancient etruscan god Tarchies . He and the nymph Vacu seem to be two of the survivors of the disappearance of Atlantis, who would have given their knowledge to the Etruscans .
name: La stirpe maledetta

description: Police asks the detectiveof impossible for help to solve a mysterious case of teleportation : a man, after having committed a murder in a house in Providence suddenly finds himself in Grand Central Terminal in New York . On the whole disturbing story hovers the figure of HP Lovecraft ...
name: La casa ai confini del mondo

description: On a mission to Venice to meet a courier, Nathan finds himself involved in a mysterious disappearance that involves Liz, wife of Martin Altman, a friend from school, and archaeologist who is there to investigate strange artifacts of a civilization that developed in parallel with the human one.
name: Fantasmi a Venezia

description: Short book (32 pages) distributed together with Speciale Nathan Never #3.
name: Miraggi

description: Short book (32 pages) distributed together with Speciale Nathan Never #4.
name: Arriva Legs!

description: Short book (32 pp.) distributed together with Speciale Nathan Never #2
name: Le mura di Blackwall

description: As Orcus and his army attack Tallus, Sela and company want to take action. But Druanna has her own way of dealing with the enemy. Who she is, and just how powerful she is, has been kept a secret until now. But Orcus has a card hidden up his evil sleeve as well. It's a standoff that will echo through the ages, through legends, and through Grimm Fairy Tales.

The beast is revealed and the remaining survivors are forced to make their escape into the forest. A forest where the beast may very well be the least of their problems. The final confrontation between the wolf and Britney is here and only one of them is getting out alive. With an ending that no one will see coming and fans will be talking about for years don't miss the conclusion of the first story arc to this hot new series.

name: Zio Paperone e l'affare dei datteri d'oro
Topolino e l'interminabile domenica
Zio Paperone e il prezioso liquido

description: After a strange party of half-starved wanderers make their way to the weather-changing station, it is soon learned they they've created their own bloody swath across the icy wastelands of the Antarctic while being pursued by rabid vampires. Meanwhile, what secret does the WWII torpedo discovered in the ice hide, and why is there something knocking on the inside of it?

Jason Delandro and his Group for the Liberation of the Mutates are taking possession of the ship " Scarlet Meteor" , commanded by General Shea , last hope of salvation for the Earth , threatened by Gothmog asteroid. Nathan Never , Yvonne Samson , Captain Mark Cameron and Captain Storm , with the help of pilot Jerry Lone , will be able to penetrate into the spaceship , but they will have to deal with the interests of the Space Liberation Front , an organization that fights for the autonomy of the orbiting stations.

Together with this special issue there was a book called "Cronache dal Futuro", a one-shot guide to the Nathan Never's Universe
name: Il giorno della meteora

description: Far away, in a land long ago...there was an orphaned farm kid with daddy issues trying to rescue an orphaned princess unaware of her daddy issues! In the tradition of ROBOT CHICKEN: STAR WARS and SPACEBALLS comes a loving, affectionate parody of the greatest science fiction franchise of all time! The first of a two-issue mini-series, this is a fan-pleasing romp that skewers one of the greatest adventure stories ever!
name: "Far Away, in a Land Long Ago..."

description: Sada, the wife of Aristotle Skotos, puts Jack O'Ryan on the footsteps of his real mother, Rachel. Together with Nathan and April, Jack goes to Bel Nakbar to interrogate the former driver of Skotos, who can provide the last address of Rachel. On the place they find the men of Skotos, who are quickly eliminated by a killer . Someone else is interested in finding out where Rachel is...
name: Legami di sangue

description: Get ready for some electrifying lightsaber battle action! Aurra Sing arrives on Coruscant with a mean streak, killing Jedi within the very shadows of the Temple. The Jedi Council must now decide how to deal with the infamous bounty hunter whose favorite targets are Jedi. Several Jedi Knights volunteer for the honor of bringing Sing to justice. But do they want justice, or vengeance? It's going to take more than a grudge to bring down an assassin with a reputation for killing Jedi and a collection of previously owned lightsabers to back it up.
name: Star Wars: The Hunt for Aurra Sing

volume.name: Star Wars: The Hunt for Aurra Sing

description: Nathan , on holiday from work , knows the charming Hadija Hab'Ahmal , currently host of a rented flat on the floor under his apartment . The two , having overcome the initial suspicion , fall in love . But Hadija , a computer expert who works for Tice , a car company , is among the suspects of sabotage against the cars produced by Tice . Alfa Agency is responsible for the investigation , particularly agents April and May.
name: Hadija

description: Ki-Adi-Mundi's first assignment after joining the Jedi Council will take him back to the fearsome desert wastelands of Tatooine. The Jedi Council has tracked a long wayward and powerful Jedi, Sharad Hett of the Sand People, to the backwater world, and it's up to Ki to find him and convince him to return. Only two things stand in his way: the vicious krayt dragon of Tatooine and the Jedi-slaying bounty hunter Aurra Sing! Ki has little choice but to ask for help from the slimiest crime lord of them all, Jabba the Hutt -- and Jabba's aid always comes with a price!
name: TPB

description:
As an ancient, unknowable evil claws its way into our world, Vampirella must stand alone...or all that lives will suffer and die. With Dracula's minions pursuing their own agendas, and legions of tentacular horrors from beyond reality scrabbling for a foothold on the material plane, only one thing is certain: there will be blood...

General Notes

On the final page of the issue there is an advertisement for The Boys (also published by Dynamite), seen as an ad on a telephone pole with a picture of Butcher and the heading "The Boys". Another paper is seen fluttering through the breeze with the heading "Monica", what this refers to is unknown.
name: Crown of Worms, Part 6

description: Jedi Knight Quinlan Vos has lost his memory. Not only must he fight to rediscover his past, he must also track down his Padawan, Aayla Secura, who has mysteriously disappeared. With only his lightsaber and a scheming Devaronian named Villie to help him, Quin must face off against deadly gamblers, false Jedi, corrupt officials, and the pull of the dark side if he is to survive! Features Jedi Quinlan Vos' introduction to the Star Wars comics story.
name: Star Wars: Twilight

description: Ki-Adi-Mundi is a Jedi Knight of formidable strength and influence. On his homeworld of Cerea, most of the planet's citizens are happy to continue their low-tech lives of simplicity, isolated from the Republic, but a growing voice calls for the advanced technologies brought by offworlders. When Ki becomes a strong voice of opposition for such development, he is falsely charged with murder and is swiftly drawn into a web of conspiracy and intrigue that could rock the galaxy to its foundations--a web that may have the vile crime lord Jabba the Hutt and the powerful Trade Federation at its center, setting the stage for Episode I --The Phantom Menace!
name: Star Wars: Prelude to Rebellion

description: In a time after the events of Episode I The Phantom Menace, half of the Jedi High Council travel to the exotic world of Malastare to negotiate a peace treaty between two of that planets warring factions. But the whole affair is being manipulated by a secret, third party out to assassinate the Jedi! Add in the fact that Malastare is one of the few planets to allow the dangerous sport of Podracing and you can be sure that the Jedi are in for some extreme action! This story features many familiar characters from The Phantom Menace and continues the ongoing adventures that bridge the gap between Episodes I & II!
name: TPB

description: Despite his successful completion of previous missions, the Jedi Council still feels that Quinlan Vos, a troubled Jedi struggling to regain stability after having his memory erased, walks dangerously close to the dark side. But when a prison planet under watch by the Guardians is attacked by an unidentified enemy, Quinlan Vos is specifically requested to investigate because of his Guardian ancestry. Fully-recovered, or not, Quin is off on another suicide mission! Collecting the four-issue story arc.
name: Star Wars: Darkness

description: Before the outbreak of the Clone Wars, the Jedi were involved in another major battle: the Stark Hyperspace War. Smuggler and pirate Iaco Stark's "commercial combine" has disrupted the production of bacta, the most important healing agent in the galaxy. By cornering the market on bacta, Stark hopes to amass a fortune. But other forces within the Republic have aligned themselves with the Trade Federation, and are hoping to use Stark's aggression as an excuse for military build-up. It's up to the members of the Jedi Council to untangle the many deceits and intrigues and bring the criminals to justice before the galaxy is plunged into war!
name: The Stark Hyperspace War

volume.name: Star Wars: The Stark Hyperspace War

description: Written by the creative talents behind the blockbuster motion picture, these exclusive one-shots tell the tales of the movie characters before the events of the film. What were Hal Jordan, Sinestro, Kilowog, Abin Sur and The Guardians all doing before the curtains rise on June 17? Experience it all in these one-shots, as told by the superstar Green Lantern movie team including producer Geoff Johns (GREEN LANTERN, THE FLASH), screenwriter Michael Goldenberg, producer/screenwriter Greg Berlanti, producer Donald De Line, screenwriter Michael Green (SUPERMAN/BATMAN) and screenwriter Marc Guggenheim (JUSTICE SOCIETY OF AMERICA)!
name: To Build a Better Lantern

description: Written by the creative talents behind the blockbuster motion picture, these exclusive one-shots tell the tales of the movie characters before the events of the film. What were Hal Jordan, Sinestro, Kilowog, Abin Sur and The Guardians all doing before the curtains rise on June 17? Experience it all in these one-shots, as told by the superstar Green Lantern movie team including producer Geoff Johns (GREEN LANTERN, THE FLASH), screenwriter Michael Goldenberg, producer/screenwriter Greg Berlanti, producer Donald De Line, screenwriter Michael Green (SUPERMAN/BATMAN) and screenwriter Marc Guggenheim (JUSTICE SOCIETY OF AMERICA)!
name: Forbidden Planet

volume.name: Green Lantern Movie Prequel: Tomar Re

description: A royal heir has been kidnapped -- along with Jedi Master Tholme, who was protecting the boy. Now two of Tholme's former Padawans have teamed up to rescue their Master, unaware of the forces arrayed against them. Their most immediate foes are a father and son team of Morgukai assassins, who have the training and the weapons to go toe-to-toe with Jedi. But behind it all are the machinations of the notorious Count Dooku!
name: Star Wars: Rite of Passage

description: The War for the Uncharted Territories continues! And even though the alliance against the Kkore has a new partner, it only makes this strange collection of bedfellows even stranger. The battle rages on while the fate of Crichton, Aeryn, and the Peacekeepers hangs in the balance!
name: The War For the Uncharted Territories Part 8: Getting the Band Back Together

description: Watch the fall of the Republic through the eyes of Sagoro Autem - Senate Guard, mercenary, prisoner, Clone Wars hero and Imperial target - in a story that spans from before the Clone Wars to the first mission of Darth Vader! Young Jedi Knight Obi-Wan Kenobi, and Anakin Skywalker, his even younger Padawan, protect a senator from a small system as assassination attempts threaten to silence his crucial swing vote. Joining the Jedi in their mission is Autem, loyal Senate Guard. Yet, as Obi-Wan and Anakin fend off a league of master assassins, Autem discovers a link between the killers that will change his own life forever - a secret he will not be able to face until the Clone Wars have come and gone, and he finds himself on the run from the new Emperor's enforcer, Darth Vader!
name: TPB

description: Claudio must battle betrayal from within his own ranks as his crew careens headlong into the final showdown with House Atlantic. But Claudio, Ambellina, and Inferno could never have imagined the surprise Wilhelm Ryan has in store for them Coheed & Cambrias Claudio Sanchez and Peter David bring you Part 1 of the exciting conclusion to this sci-fi epic!

volume.name: The Amory Wars: In Keeping Secrets of Silent Earth: 3

description: In an era when lineage defined you, three teenagers must make their way through the world hiding their identities in order to find their destinies. As their village burns behind them, they are headed for a city they'd heard about only in stories. The three young samurai must now struggle to stay alive and take vengeance on the evil usurper who has destroyed the rest of their clan and the only world they'd ever known. Will they rise on the tides of vengeance, or they will they fall on the swords of fate?

The continuing adventures of comicdoms favorite super-couple! The Crusader has faced many menaces in his career: the Fearleader, the Weather Witch, and, of course, the Evil Brain. But is he ready to face his toughest opponent yet: The United States Tax Code? It's a battle royale for the world's most powerful accountant.

The Thinker is destroyed and the world is in chaos, and Logan wants nothing to do with it. But the world isn't done with him yet and when the lives of Jessica and his son Jaq are put in jeopardy, Logan must once again don his armor. Logan's Run: Aftermath continues Logan's epic journey as he races towards an uncertain destiny...

This is not a war. It's a massacre. The Chinese army is decimated. The countryside smolders in ashes. Nothing and no one has stopped the formics. Bombs, tanks, troops. Fail. Fail. Fail. Until now. Mazer Rackham has teamed up with the Mobile Operations Police, the super elite special forces unit that previously rejected him. Their plan? Destroy a formic lander. How? By going deep underground, down in the formic tunnels . . . where swarms of formics are ready and waiting. Will they turn the tide of war or dig their own graves? The exciting prequel to Ender's Game continues.

An even more than usual melancholyc Dylan starts flipping old memories in the closet of his house . The picture of a little girl , Spring Shorend , known at school , drives him to the Scottish village of Crossgate , on the edge of Loch Whirl.
Behind the lake waters, Dylan and Spring rediscover the civilization of the Watermen, the custodians of the eternal mystery of water , and doing so he is once more the child he used to be.
In his past , under the armor that the years have built, there is still the magic of hope .
name: Il lago nel cielo

description: An apocalyptic fire in a factory in Madagascar awakens Pey , a demon scavenger , which "enters " in a vacuum cleaner . A year later , the " haunted " cleaner falls into the hands of Timothy Penderwhile , a meek salesman , who is ringing at the door of 7, Craven Road.
name: Morte a domicilio

description: Dropped at night by his last " love of his life ," Dylan finds himself along a infinite highway ( in spite of every road sign indicates a distance of 6.66 miles from London ) , in which the only other appearances are those of a mysterious ( and threatening ) black truck , Alga, a beautiful hitchhiker , a group of young boys who enjoy throwing stones from a bridge over the highway and various zombies , monsters and talking skeletons... All told ( or invented ? ) by a sleepless Groucho.
name: La strada verso il nulla

description:
Despair and madness take over the "Lost Children", now crumbling old, and so, in an attempt to regain their lost youth they rape Tinker Bell, the fairy. But fairies not necessarily have to be ethereal creatures, devoted to the good: The revenge of Tinker Bell will leave no escape.

A "politically incorrect" version of the classic Peter Pan tale.
name: Il battito del tempo

description: Alongside mankind lives , since the most ancient times , the race of " Daimonoi " . Reduced to a flicker from the medieval persecution , now they struggle to survive, despite their small number .
name: La nuova stirpe

description: Grandpa Elf tells their grandchildren the tale of Dylan Dog , of the "Great People " ...
name: Il gigante

description: What if there was a drug that gave you the power to fly? How far would you go to possess it and who would you hurt to get your next fix? This is the story of Eddie Patron. Eddie was trying to live a normal life. A rundown broken life but a normal life nonetheless. But Eddie has a secret and that secret is coming back to haunt him and his life will never be the same again. From the mind of Raven Gregory, writer of Image Comics THE GIFT, the Wonderland trilogy and The Waking comes the latest brand new ongoing tale of horror and first tale of a world where the superheroes aren't heroes at all. Don't miss what is guaranteed to be the hottest new series of the year!

Dylan runs into a young woman dying , lying on the pavement of an alley in London. After bringing the girl to the hospital , he discovers that the cause of his illness is not the easiest to trace. It will face a psychotic doctor , a demon of consciousness , a series of absurd suicides . Until the revelation of a "truth " even more difficult to understand ...
name: Il sonno della ragione

description: A wave of murders plagues the espers present in London at a conference on the subject. Dylan unfolds the tangle , and saves the esper Clarice Anderson from the fate that has struck her colleagues
name: Percezioni extrasensoriali

description: Marlon Ashbee , an elder landowner, calls Dylan Dog to Ancient Rock , to investigate about some heinous crimes committed in the surrounding countryside . Soon the suspicions gather toward a mysterious figure , the druid, who , seventeen years before , had Ashbee privated of the use of his legs .
name: Il druido

description: What's better: an ugly reality or beautiful fantasy? This is the question the Doctor is forced to confront in a medieval fantasy world where Amy finds herself reluctantly cast as a damsel in distress.
name: A Fairytale Life, Part 3

description: Life likes to be confused with Death and , most importantly, to confuse the protagonists of the story: Dylan , Angel and her father Jarvis. A race toward a grotesque fate with a special appearance by an old acquaintance : the resurrected Jackal , serial killer with existential problems .
name: ll sorriso dell'Oscura Signora

description: A cargo of radioactive waste, and a sea park where the only known specimen of giant squid is exposed , appear mysteriously in connection ...
name: Il dio prigioniero

description: Dylan finds himself memoryless is in the perfect world of Joy , which is not the best of all possible worlds. This monad has no windows , but our hero manages to escape anyway, because Joy simply does not exist...
name: Il mondo perfetto

description: A young artist is oppressed by a religious mother and a possessive husband . One night one of her statues comes alive and starts killing all the people who are despairing its creator .
name: La donna urlante

description: What mysterious parallel binds the Isle of Dogs , a peninsula jutting into the Thames in modern London in 2000 and a remote South Sea island in the far 1700? The ghost of Captain Moore has just returned to help Dylan to shed light on the enigma.
name: L'Isola dei Cani

description: Serenity is a juicy apple with a glowing skin. But as every Eden, it has its snake, this apple has a worm that feeds inside it. Dylan Dog will give a name to the worm and uncover the secrets of the idillic community founded by Dr Westwood.
name: Sopravvivere all'Eden

description: Ely Edelgase , an archaeologist, unearthed the head of the Medusa and the Perseus's shield . A series of supernatural events lead to suppose that Ely, despite hemself , awakened the spirit of the Gorgon itself ... or that she has acquired the powers .
name: Medusa

description: Simon , an aerobics instructor with a quiet life begins to be haunted by strange visions , as " memories " of murders apparently committed by him...
name: Il fiume dell'oblio

description: At the testamentary request of a thriller writer, Dylan Dog agrees to spend a month in his house, adapting to his lifestyle ( ie : the most complete solitude), in order to capture the serial killer who murdered the writer.
name: Lo specchio dell'anima

description: Pearl is a beautiful young girl with a dark past : she was in fact a " Little Death " , a powerful human scanner that someone wanted to use as a terrifying biological weapon . Her brother, whose powers of scanner are collapsing, and her abusive stepfather are still haunting Pearls present, but the girl has three tricks up his sleeve : a friend named Dylan, a boy that she loves, and Death , of whom she is the designated successor.
name: La Piccola Morte

description: The beautiful astronaut Kay Harrison claims to have been possessed by the devil during his last spacewalk, but is it possible that hell is in the heavens? Dylan Dog has the dangerous task to find ou.
name: Possessione diabolica

description: Who is slaughtering the Pennycoats? Is Duncan really alive and thirsty for revenge? And where is Hezel Pennycoat? Dylan Dog will, of course, dissolve these puzzles and those, far more distressing, about those who are holders of the Notes from Underground.
name: Memorie dal sottosuolo

description: Someone asks the money to the banks , someone steals them , as the three absurd robbers , and someone else gives them to others, putting the world upside down until it is hell on Earth, as the tender Sir Goodman. Will Dylan resist the dark fascination of money ?
name: Per un pugno di sterline
Il seme della follia
Il "progetto"
Il discepolo

description: Aaron Jethro is madly in love but a love that desires the death of its object . So when Aaron gets to use an ancient magical rite to involve many others in his folly , it becomes inevitable that Dylan crosses his path .
name: Lettere dall'Inferno

description: What happens if a stressed serial killers hunter who neglects his lovely wife asks Dylan Dog for help in an investigation ? Nothing good...
name: La terza faccia della medaglia
